  • FEATURE: Web Worker supports resetSegments

  • IMPROVEMENT: canvas renderer signifcantly improved in performance

  • IMPROVEMENT: text renderer performance improvement when rendering out of the work area
  • FIX: canvas expressions render order

V 5.12.0

  • FIX: play / pause behavior on worker
  • IMPROVEMENT: move text rendering to render phase
  • FEATURE: expose global object _lottieGlobal for expressions

- Type safety improved without breaking existing code

Closes #12

title: 🔒 Fix inconsistent and insecure token storage
body:
## Description

This PR addresses issue #10 by implementing secure token storage using the SecurityService instead of plain text localStorage.

## Changes Made

- **AuthContext.tsx**: Updated to use SecurityService for encrypted token storage
- **storageUtils.ts**: Fixed environment variable access to use `import.meta.env` for Vite compatibility
- **env.d.ts**: Added VITE_SECRET_KEY to TypeScript environment interface
- **Security**: Removed hardcoded fallback for better security

## Security Improvements

- Tokens are now encrypted before storage in localStorage
- Environment variable access is properly configured for Vite
- Fail-fast approach if VITE_SECRET_KEY is not configured
- Consistent token storage across the application

## Testing

- [ ] Verify token encryption/decryption works correctly
- [ ] Test login/logout functionality
- [ ] Ensure environment variable is properly configured

Closes #10
